<br>
Sandrat looked at each of them in turn, peering into their hearts.  They had come for a single purpose, though many did not know it yet.<br>
<br>
&quot;Look around you, my friends.  Standing beside you is another, who feels as you do.  Then look at the world that we have inherited.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;It has changed.  It is darker, more dangerous.  Unholy alliances are made these days.  We have learned in the past that we could not trust those not of humanity.  Now we know those not of humanity will indeed ally themselves with each other, and take that which does not belong to them.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;They do not care about us.  they do not care about whether we live or die.  We are just mosquitos to them.  Elves, Trolls, Halflings, they join together, to grow powerful, with no loyalties to any but their own.  A halfling will heal a troll that kills a halfling.  An elf will cut down a darkelf using magics provided by a dark elf.  they have no loyalties.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;  They have no heart.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot; I say to you, that the darkness of night is here.  However, dawn does follow night, as has always been.  The Tribe stands ready to fight.  We stand ready to defend humanity.  Long we have been without a home, and now we say NO MORE.  We will make our own home.  And we will kill those that would do us harm, no matter who they might be.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;But we are outnumbered, outskilled, with rusty weapons compared to the might of those arrayed against us.  They kill dragons, while we try to hold our own against goblins.  We are 5 nations, each alone, holding a torch against the darkness.&quot;  <br>
<br>
&quot; And the darkness will snuff us out, one by one.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Together, though, we will make a fire such as this land has never seen.  Together, we can stand before our enemies, and take back that which is ours.  Together, we can push the darkness back into the hole from which it was spawned.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Do you have the heart?  Do you have what it will take to stand against their legions?  Do you have what it will take to fight them, to see that we are not misquitos, but rather bears to be feared? DO YOU HAVE THE HEART TO FIGHT BACK?&quot;<br>
<br>
As one the people in front of him cheered.  He cold sense in them the desire, the desire to stand against the tide that had befallen the land.  They only needed a guide.<br>
<br>
